Man, I really fell in love with their first album a few months ago. At first when I got this album I was immediately disappointed. Then recently I decided to actually stop and listen to it... now I really like it. 
They went from being virtuosic indie-prog sounding mess with guitar tapping and drum blasts all over the place to something that sounds more like Band of Horses and TV On The Radio combined.
